      <title>银行寻求 AT1 替代者，以应对今年最大的转型</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-28/belfius-bank-seeks-at1-bond-in-one-of-year-s-biggest-turnarounds</link>
      <description><![CDATA[贝尔菲乌斯银行 (Belfius Bank SA) 和巴登-符腾堡州银行 (Landesbank Baden-Wuerttemberg) 正在寻求新的额外一级资本来偿还债券，这些债券之前看似可能会违背市场的提前还款传统，但却成为了今年表现最好的债券。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-28/belfius-bank-seeks-at1-bond-in-one-of-year-s-biggest-turnarounds</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 28 Oct 2024 10:41:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
